#: docs/en/news/posts/2022/buzz/october-2022-status-update.md:68
msgid ""
"Want to get involved? Here's 8 open issues that would be a great place to "
"get started with contributing to a BeeWare project. They're all relatively "
"minor changes, but would provide a big improvement to the lives of BeeWare "
"users:"
