"to be platform aware and make it so ``dev web`` utilises editbale installs "
"to serve your project to the brower making it so with simple refresh of the "
"browser you can quickly see your changes instead of waiting for a full wheel "
"rebuild."
msgstr ""

#: docs/en/news/posts/2025/buzz/2025-curtin-capstone-year-end-blog.md:1
